Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The KC Grand Prix Semi-Finals have begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It appears that Sieg stormed his way right into the Finals as soon as the match began,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Rebecca and Leon are locked in a fierce Duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}both sides not moving an inch and using all of their strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'd like to go cheer for her right away, but my grandpa went missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like he was kidnapped by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm on my way to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Leon In Fairy Tale Land"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks freakin' {\i1}delicious{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's steamed shrimp tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've even got Peking duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-The hell?!\N -The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsie-daisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Sugoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Grandpa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! That hurts, Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, my precious Vivi-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, what's the meaning of this?! Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were really worried about you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you say anything more, Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is between Yugi and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to hold the {\i1}true{\i0} Final Match of the KC Grand Prix here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this holy ground where Yugi and I will share a passionate battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost to Rebecca in the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the winner of the KC Grand Prix gets to fight against Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Dueling, as long as both mutual parties want to do it, it can happen anywhere, anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Yugi~?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't fight against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be like that, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and Duel against Vivi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be, Gramps?!\N Is she holding your life hostage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, there's an explanation for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rock-{\i0}Xiansheng{\i1}~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, Sugoroku Mutou-{\i0}Xiansheng{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Wei{\i1}, Sugoroku-{\i0}Xiansheng{\i1}, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the grandfather of the infamous Yugi, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Yes I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, will you listen to a request Vivian has of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll listen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as you can see, my waist is in a lot of pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I make that waist of yours all better, will you listen to me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoo! Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a deal~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My waist doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fortune enough to have had Vivi-{\i1}chan{\i0} come heal my back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely more to it than {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty obvious she's got the old man on a leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Gramps! That's pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is how it is, I'm not gonna be your student anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't...? I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My waist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just returned him to how he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! If you want me to heal your grandfather's back again, Duel against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low, ya creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the kind of woman who will do anything in the face of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find true love through Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Sounds lovely, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no reason to face her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no helping it. Let's help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for my grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there will be one additional condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, you will become my slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}love slave{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, you tramp! What kinda "KC Final" is this supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kinda "slave" is he supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making any sense here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him take care of this quickly so we can go root for Becky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you Dueling worth 4,000 years of China's history!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Pot of Greed from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And draw two cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Summon Witch of the Black Forest in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witch of the Black Forest, get rid of the Pumpkin Carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Cinderella lost her ability to Direct Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cinderella, attack Witch of the Black Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Witch of the Black Forest's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is sent to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can add a Monster with 1500 Defense Points or less from my deck into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Tom Thumb in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I set a card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Ruby Dragon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate a Magic Card from my hand, Dragon's Flame Bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Magic Effect of Dragon's Flame Bullets,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can destroy one face-up Monster with 800 Defense Points or less!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And using Ruby Dragon, I attack Tom Thumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Nullification!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It negates your attack and ends the Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, this boy is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Fight!\N -Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. I'm not alone out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all cheering for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep at it, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card from my hand! Giant's Training!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he's been on the field for one turn, I can tribute Tom Thumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can then Summon Globberman in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Globberman, attack Ruby Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope of Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster is sent to the Graveyard as a result of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can discard my entire hand to activate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon the Monsters with an increase of 800 Attack and Defense Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no cards in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can Special Summon Ruby Dragon without doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I open my other reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of Adamantine Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lets me sacrifice a Special Summoned Dragon-Type Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Special Summon Diamond Head Dragon from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Head Dragon's Attack Power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:12:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is determined by the total Attack Power of the sacrificed Monster plus 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 3400 Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn is this good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a unique flavor this dish has!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go cheer for Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we need to! It's obvious Yugi's gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should eat some, too! It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yup!\N -Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivian just pulled out some kinda trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Master Kyonshee and Kung-Fu Nyan Nyan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to activate the Magic Card, Luminous Cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Dragon Lady in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot Special Summon any other Monsters this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Equipment Magic from my hand, Lightning Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Lady's Attack Power increases by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Dragon Lady will attack Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can attack twice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster equipped with Lightning Saber, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can halve its own Attack Power in order to attack a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Big Shield Gardna in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place a card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You doin' okay, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!\N Like he'd be scared of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Lady attacks Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick-Play Magic! Snowfall Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Equipment Magic that only activates with a Warrior-Type Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It negates the opponent's Magic or Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it destroys the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this getting pretty bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's able to Direct Attack with two strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I activate a Magic Card from my hand, Flying Dragon Whirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending four Dragon-Type Monsters from my deck into the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can raise Dragon Lady's Attack Power up by 1200 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Lady, attack Yugi directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my~! I'm gonna win~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By discarding the Kuriboh card from my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the player's damage can be reduced to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~! I was sooo close~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'll have to end it next turn~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't {\i1}be{\i0} a next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this turn, Vivian, I'm going to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's no way you could do that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Skilled Dark Magician in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate Pot of Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw two cards from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I activate Emblem of Dragon Destroyer from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I add Buster Blader from the Graveyard into my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That light is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spell Counters. They are tallies for the activation of a magical spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Reincarnation of the Dead from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It allows me to add a Monster from the Graveyard into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Spell Counter tallies at three,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tribute Skilled Dark Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Special Summon Black Magician in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I'm fusing the Black Magician on my field with the Buster Blader in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mighty Magic Swordsman - Black Paladin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Paladin's Attack Power
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,increases by 500 points for every Dragon-Type Monster on the field and in the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have four Dragons in my Graveyard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Paladin, attack Dragon Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond Magic! Fierce Slashing Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Awright!\N -Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please heal my grandpa's waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Go for it!\N -You can do it, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you alright, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have 100 Life left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay! Because Darling came to cheer for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Head Dragon, attack Globberman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-She did it!\N -She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not one-sided anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My reverse card is Dragon's Imperial Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if my opponent uses Defense Position,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if my Monster's Attack Power surpasses that Monster's Defense Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the difference in damage will be inflicted on my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless he plays a Monster holding more than 2500 Defense Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'm going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card from my hand, Gold Moon Coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving these to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I activate Gold Moon Coin, I give all the remaining cards in my hand to my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then draw the same number of cards from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning Wheel Spindle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had used this, you would have been able to destroy a Monster on my field?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you Summon a Monster with 900 or more Attack Points on the next turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm betting on the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's very quiet, but I can sense a lot of vigor from this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, One Hundred Year Awakening, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Curse of Thorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to Special Summon Thorn Princess from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thorn Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Thorn Princess' Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Summoned, I can take control over one of the opponent's Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using Diamond Head Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I attack you directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Rebecca!\N -Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}, we have completed the background check on Sieg Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm sorry, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations. You better win the Final Match so you can face Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess even Rebecca says good things here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a hell of a better sport than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a great job, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost because you didn't get here earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca sure has a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Like you can say that!\N -Like you can say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only Jounouchi, but even Rebecca lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0} will end up fighting against Sieg in the Final Match.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, we'll be rooting for Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best for the others and win the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} suddenly stopped the two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} is going to Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaiba's Intrusion!\N The Grand Prix Final"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
